{"tid":102352,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我朋友漏左個袋係直通巴","createTime":"2017-01-31T14:34:06.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-01T05:46:40.000Z","uid":24295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5d330d0c283300eb6d40184276f8dbd708bc6f1b","tid":102352,"uid":24295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T14:34:06.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n我的朋友（真係不是我）<br />\n今日下午漏左個黑色ysl化妝袋<br />\n係架直通巴度<br />\n車牌mt3645，車號113<br />\n係車既後段.<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/31/223216_0ce3d25cbf0e6f5ae8595c8540a81b8c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F31%2F223216_0ce3d25cbf0e6f5ae8595c8540a81b8c.jpg&h=1634b0be&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我朋友係上水落左車<br />\n之後打過去總站冇人聽<br />\n入面有證件....<br />\n<br />\n連登有愛，如果有巴打執到可唔可以比返我朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aadfce45af1f6b481426eb1cd370e7dffad6a6ce","tid":102352,"uid":17279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T14:35:40.000Z","msg":"幫推 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8806f7b944ebae23fa2ec1f85d50c0f4d4b4131d","tid":102352,"uid":2311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T14:36:28.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"b6ea76e103b6913fd6074daf4302f633ecb748de","tid":102352,"uid":74162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T14:37:26.000Z","msg":"幫柚子推一推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c671844eb9d69fdc540b651febc45702a47fe3d","tid":102352,"uid":33333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T14:37:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f91a73f4e407c2e20045770865e5308aabd02572","tid":102352,"uid":34270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T14:37:57.000Z","msg":"留個靚名跟進"},{"pid":"092fb17a7d6d52b0aa54c92b0b652ac6c0e9c